### Search by country and itemType

Url: 
/items/query/{country}/{itemType}

### Update Item


required attributes 
  - **pk** 
  - **data**

#### Update data attribute 

```json
{

    "pk":"#PY#BASIC_CREDENTIALS#AMAZON_PRIME#FOX#939259bb09",
    "data":{
        "user":"new-user-user-new1-21222",
        "pass":"new-pass-user-new2-21222"
    }

}
```

#### Update MSISDN type 

```json
{

    "pk":"#CO#MSISDN#MI_tienda#backofficeco#77a446c72c",
    "data":{
        "msisdn":"571230434545465"
    },
    "planName":"POST_PAGO"
}
```
